{"data":{"markdownRemark":null,"npmPackage":{"name":"gatsby-remark-highlights","description":"Adds syntax highlighting to code blocks at build time using Atom Highlights","keywords":["gatsby","gatsby-plugin","highlight","atom","atom highlights","remark"],"lastPublisher":{"name":"amitpatra","avatar":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/8b0648b04f5174fce8a29da986fee32b"},"repository":{"url":"https://github.com/amitpatra/gatsby-remark-highlights"},"readme":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"gatsby-remark-highlights\"><a href=\"#gatsby-remark-highlights\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gatsby-remark-highlights</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://greenkeeper.io/\"><img src=\"https://badges.greenkeeper.io/amitpatra/gatsby-remark-highlights.svg\" alt=\"Greenkeeper badge\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://travis-ci.org/amitpatra/gatsby-remark-highlights\"><img src=\"https://travis-ci.org/amitpatra/gatsby-remark-highlights.svg?branch=master\" alt=\"Build Status\"></a></p>\n<p>Adds syntax highlighting to code blocks in markdown files using <a href=\"https://github.com/atom/highlights\">Atom highlights</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"install\"><a href=\"#install\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Install</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npm install --save gatsby-transformer-remark gatsby-remark-highlights</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-use\"><a href=\"#how-to-use\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How to use</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\">\n      <pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// In your gatsby-config.js</span>\nplugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-transformer-remark`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-remark-highlights`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n          options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">// Additional languages, no need to add it </span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">// if you don't wish to use additional languages</span>\n              additionalLangs<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`language-rust`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">// scope prefix to use, defaults to ''</span>\n              scopePrefix<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'syntax--'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n              codeWrap<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n                className<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'midnight'</span>\n              <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>To use additional languages, you have to install them via <code class=\"language-text\">npm</code>\ne.g to use Rust install <code class=\"language-text\">language-rust</code> package</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npm install language-rust</code></p>\n<p>It supports any language that is supported by Atom.\nFor language packages, please visit <a href=\"https://atom.io/packages/\">Atom packages</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"include-css\"><a href=\"#include-css\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Include CSS</h2>\n<p>To use this plugin you have to use a Atom theme. Atom themes are <em>less</em> files so you have to compile them. Rename <code class=\"language-text\">atom-text-editor</code> to <code class=\"language-text\">editor</code> and remove every instance of <code class=\"language-text\">syntax--</code> (optional; if you donâ€™t want to do that just set the scopePrefix to <code class=\"language-text\">syntax--</code>)  in the theme files.</p>\n<h2 id=\"release-history\"><a href=\"#release-history\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Release History</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>1.3.3 Enable single quote for inline configs</li>\n<li>1.3.2 Fix for cases when grammar name is absent</li>\n<li>1.3.1 Fix line highlight bug</li>\n<li>1.3.0 Implement inline config, line highlight</li>\n<li>1.2.0 Implement code wrapping</li>\n<li>1.1.5 Code reorganization</li>\n<li>1.1.4 Bug fix, highlight when no lang is provided</li>\n<li>1.1.3 Remove highlight function</li>\n<li>1.1.2 Remove console.log</li>\n<li>1.1.1 Add lodash dependency(Bug fix)</li>\n<li>1.1.0 Support for additional languages and scope prefix added</li>\n<li>1.0.0 Initial release</li>\n</ul>","timeToRead":1}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/packages/gatsby-remark-highlights/","id":"9912bbd2-2139-595f-8ae3-704cf87b9497"}}